subs.title: Admin user must be able to create new room by filling up all mandatory fields @sanity
Admin user must NOT be able to create new room with the room name empty
Admin user must NOT be able to create new room with the room price less than 1
Customer must be able to log in to the hotel website by filling up mandatory fields @sanity
Customer must NOT be able to log in to the hotel website without filling up the username field
Customer must NOT be able to log in to the hotel website without filling up the password field
